name: Schizoid Bunny #14
description: From a love affair between a rabbit and a kangaroo, Roberto was born. He is a very strange little rabbit.  His body is different and imagine his voice! But we only say different in relation to an illusory majority. If you look deeply, into the details, you will see that we are all different. Comparisons disintegrate. Believe it or not, the only difference between Roberto and that majority is that Roberto is real.
